com.paypal.selion.platform.html.support.events

Interface ElementEventListener

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbstractElementEventListener

    public interface ElementEventListener
    Events which can occur in SeLion's AbstractElement implementations. This interface allows you to hook into those events to do customization.

        This event gets triggered before we perform a click on an element. The following objects trigger this event, Button, CheckBox, DatePicker, Form, Image, Label, Link, RadioButton, SelectList, Table, TextField
        Parameters:
        target - Instance of the element that triggered this event and implements Clickable
        expected - The expected objects that were passed to the click method
